  One thing I have toyed around with is the idea of extending the
    INT 15h/C2xxh functions to allow for multiple mice.  The functions
    are currently designed assuming a single mouse.  It would be pretty
    easy to add a few functions that would allow for basic detecting,
    disabling/enabling, exchanging of buttons, etc., for multiple mice
    at the BIOS level.  Nothing like that is implemented now, but would
    be possible to do if there was enough interest.

