      RptGDWheel           EQU   38h ;Wheel
      RptGDHatSwitch       EQU   39h ;Hat-Switch
      RptGDCountedBuff     EQU   3Ah ;Counted Buffer
      RptGDByteCount       EQU   3Bh ;Byte Count
      RptGDMotionWakeup    EQU   3Ch ;Wakeup on Motion
      RptGDStart           EQU   3Dh ;Start
